{"title_page": "Kahin Deep Jaley", "text_new": "{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = Kahin Deep Jaley\n| image                    = Kahin Deep Jaly.jpg\n| image_alt                = \n| caption                  = \n| show_name_2              = \n| native_name              = \u06a9\u06c1\u06cc\u06ba \u062f\u06cc\u067e \u062c\u0644\u06d2\n| genre                    = Romance, Family, Tragedy\n| creator                  = [[Qaisra Hayat]]\n| based_on                 = Novel of the same name\n| developer                = \n| screenplay               = \n| story                    = Qaisra Hayat\n| director                 = Sami Waseem\n| writer                   = Qaisra Hayat\n| creative_director        = \n| starring                 = {{plainlist| \n*[[Neelam Muneer]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://en.dailypakistan.com.pk/lifestyle/kahin-deep-jalays-ost-is-out-and-we-are-hooked/ |title=Kahin Deep Jalay\u2019s OST is out and we are hooked |website=Daily Pakistan Global |publisher=[[Daily Pakistan]] |location=Pakistan |access-date=2019-10-23}}</ref>\n*[[Imran Ashraf]]\n*[[Saba Faisal (actress)|Saba Faisal]]\n*[[Ali Abbas (actor)|Ali Abbas]]\n*Nazish Jahangir\n}}\n| narrated                 = \n| theme_music_composer     = Sahir Ali Bagga\n| opentheme                = \n| endtheme                 = \n| composer                 = \n| country                  = Pakistan\n| language                 = Urdu\n| executive_producer       = \n| cinematography           = \n| editor                   = \n| camera                   = [[Multi-camera setup]]\n| runtime                  = 40 minutes\n| producer                 = [[Abdullah Kadwani]]<br>Asad Qureshi\n| company                  = [[7th Sky Entertainment]]\n| distributor              = [[Geo TV]]\n| budget                   = \n| picture_format           = [[PAL]] ([[576i]])<br>[[HDTV]] [[1080i]]\n| audio_format             = [[Stereophonic sound]]\n| first_run                = <!--The nation in which the series first aired, if different from country parameter-->\n| first_aired              = {{Start date|2019|10|03|df=y}}\n| last_aired               = present\n| preceded_by              = \n| followed_by              = \n| website                  = http://harpalgeo.tv/program/Kahin-Deep-Jalay\n| production_website       = \n| num_seasons              = 1\n| num_episodes             = 25\n| network                  = [[Geo Entertainment]]\n}}\n'''''Kahin Deep Jaley''''' ''(meaning: Somewhere There is A Light)'' is a 2019 [[Pakistani dramas|Pakistani]] television series, produced by [[Abdullah Kadwani]] and [[Asad Qureshi]] under their production banner [[7th Sky Entertainment]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/535931-new-drama-serial-kaheen-deep-jaley-starts-on-geo-tv|title=New drama serial \u2018Kaheen Deep Jaley\u2019 starts on Geo TV|last=|first=|date=|website=[[The News International]]|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-10-14}}</ref> It features [[Neelam Muneer]] and [[Imran Ashraf]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/magazine/instep-today/537473-kahin-deep-jaley-explores-harsh-realities-of-life|title=Kahin Deep Jaley explores harsh realities of life|last=Shabbir|first=Buraq|date=|website=The News|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-10-14}}</ref> It airs every Thursday night on [[Geo Entertainment]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://images.dawn.com/news/1183657|title=Neelum Muneer and Imran Ashraf are playing a married couple in trouble in their next drama|last=Haq|first=Irfan Ul|date=2019-09-12|website=[[Dawn (newspaper)|DAWN]]|language=en|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/magazine/instep-today/466902-imran-ashraf-to-play-a-romantic-hero-in-his-next|title=Imran Ashraf to play a romantic hero in his next|last=Shabbir|first=Buraq|website=The News|language=en|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tns.thenews.com.pk/drama-serials-look-forward/|title=Drama serials to look forward to|last=Instep|date=2019-09-22|website=[[The News International|TNS - The News on Sunday]]|language=en-US|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/magazine/instep-today/525307-imran-ashraf-neelum-muneer-take-up-new-roles-in-this-romance|title=Imran Ashraf & Neelum Muneer take up new roles in this romance|last=Isani|first=Aamna Haider|website=[[The News International]]|language=en|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.geo.tv/latest/250341-geo-tvs-kaheen-deep-jalay-racks-up-massive-acclaim-after-first-episode|title=Geo TV's 'Kahin Deep Jalay' racks up massive acclaim after first episode|last=|first=|date=2019-10-07|website=[[Geo News]]|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2019-10-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/magazine/instep-today/479049-neelam-muneer-on-her-next-with-imran-ashraf|title=Neelam Muneer on her next with Imran Ashraf|last=Shabbir|first=Buraq|website=[[The News International]]|language=en|access-date=2019-09-29}}</ref>\n\n== Plot ==\nRida is a young lucky girl who is the only beloved sister of her 3 brothers.Faham is the oldest who raised his younger siblings after his dads death.Hatim is also very responsible but has an old-fashioned thinking,although he lives in America.Asim,is the youngest brother who loves to tease his sister Rida and says he stole his part of parents attention from him.Despite their flaws,the three brothers love Rida dearly.Shamila is a poisonous girl who dislikes her sister in law and gets jealous of Rida as her own brother does not love her as much as Rida's brothers do.She is also Faham's fiance.Zeeshan's dad dies in an acciet and a greedy business partner snatches everything from him.His uncle then gives him a job and a house.Zeeshan is invited to Fahams wedding where he stops Rida's stole from burning,and falls n love with her. Toqeer also gives Rida a letter,which Khadija puts in the study.Zeeshan's mom asks for Rida's hand in marriage where Rida's brothers refuse because Rida wants to complete her eduation.Rida's mom however says yes.Zeeshan gets possesive about Rida and on the second day of wedding Shamila asks Rida at the breakfast table that whether she loves her brothers more or Zeeshan.Zeeshan expects her to take his name but Rida takes nobody's name which offends him.Zeeshan gets typhoid and learns that he can never become a father.He starts to tourture Rida.He asks her to return her dowry,which Rida unwillingly does,her brothers get hurt and Shamila sends a recording of their conversations to Zeeshan,who gets even more possesive about Rida.Shamila goes to Rida's house and see's Rida in a poor state and comments that Zeeshan needed a maid,not a wife.Zeeshan overhears this and exposes Shamila.Zeeshan and Rida go to Murree but return as Zeeshan's mother breaks her foot.Rida remembers that Zeeshan has to get is report but Zeeshan is so scared that she will get to know his secret that he starts to scold her.Faham sends a maid to Rida's home,where Zeeshan scolds Rida and tells the maid that they do not need her.Rida finally gets angry and saysthat she is tired of his self-respect and proudness,she feels suffocated around him and she will leave him.Zeeshan's nightmare becomes reality,he apologizes to Rida.Zeeshan starts to get grumpy and ill-tempered with Rida,which his mother repramands.Rida goes to her mother's house for a visit and Zeeshan gets angry and goes to her house to tell her to come home now.He finds Toqeer's letter,and drags Rida out of his house.Faham also gets murdered.Zeeshan shows Rid's brothers the letter and they start to hate her.Rida gets to know she is pregnant.Zeeshan tells Rida he cannot become a father and his mother tells him to get another test.Zeeshan tells Rida that she is cheating on him and that the child is not his.Rida gets very hurt and vows not to forgive Zeeshan.She gets very stressed and faints.It turns out there had been a report mix up.But it is too late as Rida suffers a misscarriage.Zeeshan starts to regret this and his possesiveness on Rida.When he asks Rida's family to forgive him,Hatim shouts at him but finally agrees,but says he will only forgive him if Rida forgives him.Rida,however shuts the door on his face and says that he killed her child,and her love,respect and child are gone because of him.She further adds that even God will not forgive him till he does.This haunts Zeeshan and he starts to seek out peace and becomes religoius.\n\n==Cast==\n*[[Neelam Muneer]] as Rida\n*[[Imran Ashraf]] as Zeeshan Ahmed\n*[[Saba Faisal (actress)|Saba Faisal]] as Khadija, Rida's mother\n*[[Ali Abbas (actor)|Ali Abbas]] as Faham, Shameela's husband and Rida's elder brother\n*Nazish Jahangir as Shameela, Rida's sister-in-law (Antagonist/Second Female Lead)\n*[[Saba Hameed]] as Zeeshan's mother\n*Nida Mumtaz as Rehana, Shameela's mother and Khadija's sister\n*Beena Chaudhry as Touqeer's mother\n*[[Ali Ansari (actor)|Ali Ansari]] as Touqeer, Rushna's brother\n*Farah Nadeem as Zeeshan's aunt\n*Hammad Farooqui as Hatim, Rida's brother\n*Syed Arez as Asim, Rida's. brother\n* Madiha Rizvi as Nyla, Shameela's paternal cousin and sister-in-law\n*Hasan Noman as Salman, Shameela's brother and Nyla's husband\n*Agha Mustafa Hassan as Farhan, Rida's Cousin\n*Salma Shaheen as Zahida, Rida's family servant\n*Sarah Ali as Rushna, Rida's best friend\n*Shehzad Mukhtar as Habib, Zeeshan's uncle\n\n==Reception==\nThe show became a ratings hit in a very short span of time. Critics and audiences alike appreciated the acting of Nazish Jahangir (Shameela), Rida (Neelam Munir) and Zeeshan (Imran Ashraf). The show crossed 17+ TRPs and was the #1 show in [[Pakistan]] after ending of [[Mere Paas Tum Ho]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:2019 Pakistani television series debuts]]\n[[Category:Pakistani television sitcoms]]\n[[Category:2010s Pakistani t