{"title_page": "Hideo Ninomiya", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese swimmer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox swimmer\n| name           = Hideo Ninomiya\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| nationality    = \n| strokes        = \n| club           = \n| collegeteam    = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1937|11|28|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| medaltemplates = \n| show-medals    = \n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Hideo Ninomiya'''|\u4e8c\u5bae \u82f1\u96c4|Ninomiya Hideo|born 28 November 1937}} is a Japanese former [[Swimming (sport)|swimmer]]. He competed in the [[Swimming at the 1956 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 100 metre backstroke|men's 100 metre backstroke]] at the [[1956 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ni/hideo-ninomiya-1.html |title=Hideo Ninomiya Olympic Results |accessdate=4 October 2016}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ninomiya, Hideo}}\n[[Category:1937 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Japanese male swimmers]]\n[[Category:Olympic swimmers of Japan]]\n[[Category:Swimmers at the 1956 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Asian Games medalists in swimming]]\n[[Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Japan]]\n[[Category:Swimmers at the 1958 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1958 Asian Games]]\n{{Japan-swimming-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Japanese swimmer}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=October 2016}}\n{{Infobox swimmer\n| name           = Hideo Ninomiya\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| fullname       = \n| nationality    = \n| strokes        = \n| club           = \n| collegeteam    = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1937|11|28|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| medaltemplates = \n| show-medals    = \n}}\n\n{{Nihongo|'''Hideo Ninomiya'''|\u4e8c\u5bae \u82f1\u96c4|Ninomiya Hideo|born 28 November 1937}} is a Japanese former [[Swimming (sport)|swimmer]]. He competed in the [[Swimming at the 1956 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 100 metre backstroke|men's 100 metre backstroke]] at the [[1956 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ni/hideo-ninomiya-1.html |title=Hideo Ninomiya Olympic Results |accessdate=4 October 2016}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ninomiya, Hideo}}\n[[Category:1937 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Japanese male swimmers]]\n[[Category:Olympic swimmers of Japan]]\n[[Category:Swimmers at the 1956 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Asian Games medalists in swimming]]\n[[Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Japan]]\n[[Category:Swimmers at the 1958 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1958 Asian Games]]\n{{Japan-swimming-bio-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Lugnuts", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hideo_Ninomiya"}
